sequenceDiagram
    participant SA as Superadmin
    participant AO as Admin Ops
    participant API as Backend API
    participant DB as Database

    SA->>API: 1. Setup Master Data (Rute, Armada)
    API->>DB: Simpan Master Data
    AO->>API: 2. Buat Template Jadwal (v-model=name, route)
    API->>DB: POST /departure-scheduler
    AO->>API: 3. Klik "Generate Jadwal"
    API->>DB: POST /departure-scheduler/generate/:id
    Note right of API: Asynchronous split per tanggal
    AO->>API: 4. Assign Supir (v-model=driverId)
    API->>DB: PUT /departure-manifest/:id
    Note right of DB: Status Manifest = "Siap Dipesan"
